data.description: A tranquil oasis awaits you in this immaculate like-new retreat, where every detail has been carefully crafted to perfection. Bask in the serenity of your very own slice of paradise, complete with a coveted primary bedroom conveniently located on the first floor, ensuring both comfort and convenience. Need a space to work from home? Look no further than the versatile office space, designed to inspire productivity and creativity. And when it's time to unwind, go out to the charming screened-in porch, where gentle breezes await. With its perfect blend of comfort and functionality, this property is not just a house—it's your dream home waiting to be realized. Last thing, the seller's loan could be assumable for you. Ask us how!  Don't let this opportunity slip away—schedule your private viewing today and experience the epitome of luxurious living!
